idCitation.resTitle: M338TaxPar - Parcel data for Whitman, MA complying with Level 3 of MassGIS digital parcel standard

dataIdInfo.idPurp: The purpose of this dataset is to provide the Massachuesetts Office of Geographic Information with a polygon representation of the parcels for the Town of Whitman, Massachuesetts that comply with its Level III standards.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This dataset is a polygon representation of the parcels for the Town of Whitman, Massachusetts. Edits to a base parcel file were made to the spatial and tabular data in order to bring the file in compliance with November 2010 MassGIS Level III Standards for Digital Parcel Files. These edits included ensuring that the parcel fabric was continuous and closed with no gaps or overlaps. Additionally, parcels were snapped to the legislatively approved MassGIS TOWNSSURVEY_ARC town boundary datalayer and compared against the 2008 30 cm MassGIS Ortho Imagery. Polygons were assigned a LOC_ID that links to the M338Assessor table and other fields were populated where they were known and applicable. Annual parcel updates completed June 2024. Geometry and attribute data updated on 6/2024
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Parcel mapping data maintained by CAI Technologies

Consts.useLimit: This data may be appropriate for planning purposes. It should not be utilized where legal and surveyed property boundaries are required.
